{"text_id":188575,"tokens":["We"," study"," the"," bandit"," problem"," where"," arms"," are"," associated"," with"," stationary"," ph"," -","mixing"," processes"," and"," where"," rewards"," are"," therefore"," dependent",":"," the"," question"," that"," arises"," from"," this"," setting"," is"," that"," of"," choosing"," an"," optimal"," arm"," selection"," policy"," (","i",".","e","."," a"," policy"," that"," maximizes"," the"," expected"," cumulative"," reward",")."," We"," first"," derive"," lower"," and"," upper"," bounds"," on"," the"," optimal"," expected"," cumulative"," reward","."," We"," then"," show"," that"," for"," the"," case"," where"," the"," mixing"," rates"," of"," the"," processes"," are"," bounded"," by"," a"," known"," constant",","," there"," exists"," an"," optimal"," policy"," which"," is"," deterministic","."," The"," approach"," is"," extended"," to"," the"," case"," where"," the"," processes"," have"," finite","-","order"," moving","-","average"," representations","."," It"," is"," shown"," that"," for"," order","-","1"," processes",","," there"," exists"," a"," sub","optimal"," threshold","-","based"," policy"," that"," is"," easy"," to"," implement"," and"," that"," achieves"," the"," same"," asymptotic"," performance"," as"," the"," optimal"," policy",","," but"," with"," a"," lower"," constant"," term","."],"sub_source":"sci_gen","model":"30B","label":1}